overview: In the dawn of the sexploitation era, aspiring glamour model Ginger (Jamie Devitt) learns the only available photo assignments are for salacious men's magazines, and that she must risk eviction or must succumb to the sadistic perversions of dominating lesbian photographer Paula (Jennicka Andersson).
tagline: The Shocking Tribute To Sexploitation Cinema
title: Climb It, Tarzan!
